data.name: Label9.Text
data.value:
Transactions are the main way points get issued, redeemed, and refunded.
The standard process is as follows: 1) The merchant generates a transaction. 2) The merchant generates a receipt, or the transaction's "Token" value is somehow displayed to the customer in a QR code. 3) The customer scans their QR code with Loyaltyapp on their phone. 4) The merchant checks the status of the transactions.
Once the transaction is marked as complete, the merchant can be sure the transaction has occurred.
